Package assn6

Interface Summary
Limits This is an interface for limits in the cubbyhole example.
 

Class Summary
Coconut Simulates a coconuts that falls from a certain tree and is given a certain numerical name.
CoconutTree Simulates a tree that drops coconuts into a cubbyhole every so often, based upon a random interval
Cubby Represents a cubbyhole where coconuts are dropped and monkeys catch them and eat them.
Main This initializes a "cubbyhole", creates a coconut tree that drops coconuts, and a set of monkeys that eats coconuts, and starts the process up that the tree starts dropping coconuts and the monkeys start catching and eating coconuts.
Monkey This simulates a monkey that catches and eats a coconut using a cubbyhole.
